## [0.2.0] - 2024-09-01

### Added
- Add the server base code(server, router, error handler).
- Add the config loader.
- Add the logging system initializer.

## [0.1.1] - 2024-09-01

### Added
- Add additional core dependencies.

### Changed
- Set-up the final project layout.

## [0.1.0] - 2024-08-17

### Added
- Build the initial project layout.
- Add the package information.
- Add core dependencies.
- Add build options.